dct_title_s: Transports en commun de Bordeaux - Centre de la Ville de Bordeaux
dct_description_sm: One map on recto: Centre de la Ville. Scale = 1:10,000. Street map of center of Bordeaux. Two maps on verso. Map on left: Autobus - Réseau Suburbain - Transports en Commun de Bordeaux. Scale = 1:90,000. Map of bus routes in greater Bordeaux. Map on right: Transports en Commun de Bordeaux - Autobus - Réseau Urbain. Scale = 1:32,000. Map of bus routes in Bordeaux city.
